<pb ed="T" id="T21.1315.0466c" n="0466c"/>
<lb n="0466c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0466c02"/>
<lb n="0466c03"/><head type="no">No. 1315</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0466c04"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0466011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，【甲】三十帖策子第二十六</note>施諸餓鬼飲食及水法<note place="inline">并手印</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0466c05"/>
<lb n="0466c06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0466012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔特進…三藏〕十二字－【甲】</note><app n="0466012" word-count="12"><lem>特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>沙門
<lb n="0466c07"/>大廣智不空<note n="0466013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉詔＝三藏【甲】</note><app n="0466013"><lem>奉　詔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三藏</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0466c08"/><p>先出眾生食。事須如法。周匝種種皆著並
<lb n="0466c09"/>須淨好。或一分或少許或一器。皆須安淨銅
<lb n="0466c10"/>器中如法。如無銅器白瓷亦得。如無瓷器可
<lb n="0466c11"/>用漆器。其飲食須和清水。面向東立坐亦得
<lb n="0466c12"/>作法</p>
<lb n="0466c13"/><p>夫欲施一切餓鬼飲食者。先須發廣大心普
<lb n="0466c14"/>請餓鬼。<note n="0466014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">先＋（請）【甲】</note><app n="0466014"><lem>先</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">先請</rdg></app>誦此偈至<note n="0466015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【甲】</note><app n="0466015"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一遍。然<note n="0466016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔後〕－【甲】</note><app n="0466016"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作<note n="0466017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔召〕－【甲】</note><app n="0466017"><lem>召</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0466c15"/>請法。所獲福利果報不可校量</p>
<lb n="0466c16"/><lg><l>比丘比丘尼<note place="inline">某甲</note>發心奉持</l><l>一器淨食</l>
<lb n="0466c17"/><l>普施十方</l><l>窮盡虛空</l><l>周遍法界</l>
<lb n="0466c18"/><l>微塵剎中</l><l>所有國土</l><l>一切餓鬼</l>
<lb n="0466c19"/><l>先亡久遠</l><l>山川地主</l><l>乃至曠野</l>
<lb n="0466c20"/><l>諸鬼神等</l><l>請來集此</l><l>我今悲愍</l>
<lb n="0466c21"/><l>普施汝食</l><l>願汝各各</l><l>受我此食</l>
<lb n="0466c22"/><l>轉將供養</l><l>盡虛空界</l><l>以佛及聖</l>
<lb n="0466c23"/><l>一切有情</l><l>汝與有情</l><l>普皆飽滿</l>
<lb n="0466c24"/><l>亦願汝身</l><l>乘此&CB00057;食</l><l>離苦解脫</l>
<lb n="0466c25"/><l>生天受樂</l><l>十方淨土</l><l>隨意遊往</l>
<lb n="0466c26"/><l>發菩提心</l><l>行菩提道</l><l>當來作佛</l>
<lb n="0466c27"/><l>永莫退轉</l><l>前得道者</l><l>誓相度脫</l>
<lb n="0466c28"/><l>又願汝等</l><l>晝夜&M010527;常</l><l>擁護於我</l>
<lb n="0466c29"/><l>滿我所願</l><l>願施此食</l><l>所生功德</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1315.0467a" n="0467a"/>
<lb n="0467a01"/><l>普將&CB00327;施</l><l>法界有情</l><l>與諸有情</l>
<lb n="0467a02"/><l>平等共有</l><l>共諸有情</l><l>同將此福</l>
<lb n="0467a03"/><l>盡將迴向</l><l>真如法界</l><l>無上菩提</l>
<lb n="0467a04"/><l>一切智智</l><l>願速成佛</l><l>勿招餘果</l>
<lb n="0467a05"/><l>願<note n="0467001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乘＝我【甲】</note><app n="0467001"><lem>乘</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">我</rdg></app>此法</l><l>疾得成佛</l></lg>
<lb n="0467a06"/><p>合掌當心誦此偈。以印作召請　開喉印　以
<lb n="0467a07"/>右手大指與中指。面相捻。餘三指相去。微作
<lb n="0467a08"/>曲勢即是。名普集印　&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0467a09"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0467002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本梵字總無之</note><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝慕【甲】</note><app n="0467003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慕</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5DE;</t><t lang="chi">步</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>布</zi><sg><note n="0467004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0467004"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哩＝唎【甲】＊</note><app n="0467005"><lem>哩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唎</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A440;</t><t lang="chi">迦</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a01"/>哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝哆【甲】＊</note><app n="0467006"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a02"/>哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>他</zi><sg><note n="0467007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0467007"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0467a10"/>
<lb n="0467a11"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00617;＝揭【甲】＊</note><app n="0467008"><lem>&CB00617;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">揭</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a03"/>多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;&SD-D9C6;</t><t lang="chi">也</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0467a12"/>
<lb n="0467a13"/><p>作此印誦此&CB00057;一七遍。廣運悲心。願令法界
<lb n="0467a14"/>微塵剎中。一切餓鬼悉皆雲集</p>
<lb n="0467a15"/><p>又誦開地獄門及咽喉&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0467a16"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5DE;</t><t lang="chi">步</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>布</zi><sg><anchor id="fxT21p0467a04"/>入</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＝諦【甲】＊</note><app n="0467009"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">諦</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a05"/>哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A440;</t><t lang="chi">迦</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a06"/>哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi">他</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467a07"/>&CB00617;</t></tt>
<lb n="0467a17"/>
<lb n="0467a18"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi><anchor id="fxT21p0467a08"/>多</zi><sg><anchor id="fxT21p0467a09"/>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;&SD-D9C6;</t><t lang="chi">也</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0467a19"/>
<lb n="0467a20"/><p>誦此&CB00057;時。以左手執持食器。以右手作前召
<lb n="0467a21"/>請印。唯改一誦&CB00057;一彈指。以大指與中指頭
<lb n="0467a22"/>相捻。彈指作聲即是。餘三指開稍微曲此名
<lb n="0467a23"/>破地獄門及開咽喉印。爾時如來。即說無量
<lb n="0467a24"/>威德自在光明勝妙之力加持飲食陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0467a25"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫＝慕【甲】＊</note><app n="0467010"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慕</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">薩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B7A3;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0467011"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（去）夾註【甲】＊</note><app n="0467012"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">他<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00617;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多&CB00085;嚕吉帝＝哆引一縛路枳帝二【甲】</note>多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A652;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A442;</t><t lang="chi">吉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi">帝</t></tt>
<lb n="0467a26"/>
<lb n="0467a27"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（跋囉上跋囉三）【甲】</note><app n="0467014"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唵跋囉上跋囉三</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A6;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆羅＝跋囉【甲】</note><note n="0467015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><corr sic="婆" resp="CBETA.Maha">娑</corr>羅＝跋囉【甲】</note>娑</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A6;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆羅＝跋囉四【甲】</note>婆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA74;&SD-D9C6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>吽</zi><sg><note n="0467017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝虎叫【甲】</note><app n="0467017"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">虎叫</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0467a28"/>
<lb n="0467a29"/><p>誦此&CB00057;一七遍。一切餓鬼<note n="0467018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（各）【甲】</note><app n="0467018"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">各各</rdg></app>皆得摩伽陀國
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1315.0467b" n="0467b"/>
<lb n="0467b01"/>所用之斗<note n="0467019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467019"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七<note n="0467020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斛＝斗【甲】</note><app n="0467020"><lem>斛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">斗</rdg></app>之食。食已皆得生天或
<lb n="0467b02"/>生淨土。能令行者業障消除增益壽命。現世
<lb n="0467b03"/>獲<note n="0467021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無量無邊福＝福無量無邊【甲】</note><app n="0467021"><lem>無量無邊福</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">福無量無邊</rdg></app>。況當來世。<note n="0467022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467022"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作手印誦此
<lb n="0467b04"/><note n="0467023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0467023"><lem>真言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>加持飲食。以右手大指。摩中指甲三兩
<lb n="0467b05"/>遍。三指直<note n="0467024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔立〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467024"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>之。又以大指捻頭指。彈指作
<lb n="0467b06"/>聲。一誦&CB00057;一彈指即是</p>
<lb n="0467b07"/><p>又誦蒙甘露法味<anchor id="fxT21p0467b01"/>真言。作施無畏印。以右手
<lb n="0467b08"/>&CB00594;臂。展五指直上即是。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0467b09"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467b02"/>莫</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0BC;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘇＋（上）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0467025"><lem>蘇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蘇<note place="inline">上</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A643;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頗也＝播也二合去一【甲】</note>頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">也</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467b03"/>他</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00617;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467b04"/>多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＋（二）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0467027"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">也<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt>
<lb n="0467b10"/>
<lb n="0467b11"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A7EF;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00135;也他唵蘇＝姪嬭也反他去三唵四蘇二合【甲】</note>&CB00135;也</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi">他</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB7A;</t><t lang="chi">蘇嚕</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB7A;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘇嚕＝蘇上嚕五【甲】</note><app n="0467029"><lem>蘇嚕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蘇上嚕五</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA44;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00425;＝跋【甲】＊</note><app n="0467030"><lem>&CB00425;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跋</rdg></app>羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB7A;</t><t lang="chi">蘇<note n="0467031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＋（六）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0467031"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">嚕<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA44;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467b05"/>&CB00425;羅</t></tt>
<lb n="0467b12"/>
<lb n="0467b13"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB7A;</t><t lang="chi">蘇<note n="0467032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＋（七）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0467032"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">嚕<note place="inline">七</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑<note n="0467033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0467033"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app></zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;&SD-D9C6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi><note n="0467034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝訶【甲】</note><app n="0467034"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app></zi><sg><anchor id="fxT21p0467b06"/>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0467b14"/>
<lb n="0467b15"/><p>作前施無畏印。誦此<note n="0467035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0467035" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">&CB00057;</sic>施甘露真言一七遍。
<lb n="0467b16"/>能令飲食及水。變成無量乳及甘露。能開一
<lb n="0467b17"/>切餓鬼咽喉。能令飲食廣得增多平等得<note n="0467036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喫〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467036"><lem>喫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0467b18"/>也</p>
<lb n="0467b19"/><p>次作毘盧遮那一字心水輪觀真言<note n="0467037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467037"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。先想
<lb n="0467b20"/>此<term lang="san-sd">&SD-E1AF;</term>&CB00680;字<note n="0467038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝以【甲】</note><app n="0467038"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>右手心中。猶如乳色。變為<note n="0467039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467039"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0467b21"/>功德海。流出一切甘露醍醐。即引手臨食器
<lb n="0467b22"/>上<note n="0467040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;曰〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0467040" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">&CB00057;<note n="0467041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰誦〕－【甲】</note><note n="0467041" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>〔曰誦〕－【甲】</note>曰</sic>。誦此<term lang="san-sd">&SD-E1AF;</term><note n="0467042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00680;〕－【甲】</note><app n="0467042"><lem>&CB00680;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字一七遍。即展開五
<lb n="0467b23"/>指。向下臨食器中。觀想乳等從字中流出。猶
<lb n="0467b24"/>如日月乳海。一切鬼等皆得飽滿無有乏少。
<lb n="0467b25"/>此名普施一切餓鬼印真言曰</p>
<lb n="0467b26"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0467b07"/>莫</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿多＝漫多一【甲】</note>滿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65A;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒＝勃【甲】</note><app n="0467044"><lem>沒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">勃</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AF72;</t><t lang="chi">馱</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E040;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0467045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃&CB00680;去＝喃二縛&CB00292;二合三【甲】</note>喃</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A660;&SD-D9C6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00680;</zi><sg>去</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0467b27"/>
<lb n="0467b28"/><p>觀想誦此&CB00057;一七遍已。寫於淨地無人行處。
<lb n="0467b29"/>或水池邊樹下。唯不得寫於桃樹柳樹石榴
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1315.0467c" n="0467c"/>
<lb n="0467c01"/>樹下。寫訖更為至心。稱五如來名號三遍功
<lb n="0467c02"/>德無量</p>
